### **3. ORIENTATION SUPPORT PATTERN**

**File Paths:**
- `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775493448533-r2d7rl/apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/tabs.tsx` (horizontal/vertical)
- `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775493448533-r2d7rl/apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/separator.tsx` (horizontal/vertical)
- `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775493448533-r2d7rl/apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/slider.tsx` (horizontal/vertical)

**Tabs Example:**
```typescript
